eptember   yahoo launched a new version of the my yahoo personalized homepage the redesign allows users to tailor a homepage with widgets that access features such as email accounts calendars flickr and other yahoo content and internet content users can also select theme packs that represent artists such as polly apfelbaum and alec monopoly and bands such as empire of the sun mayer then explained at a conference in late september  that the logo change was the result of feedback from both external parties and employees logo used from january  to march  logo used from march to august  logo used from august to december  logo used from january  to june  logo used from june  to november  logo used from november  to september  logo used from september  until today see also san francisco bay area portal companies portal internet portal list of search engines list of web analytics software yahoo guesthouse yahoo litigation yahoo messenger protocol references  pitta julie april   yipee for yahoo ipo spurs trading frenzy as shares more than double los angeles times retrieved july     yahoo’s q earnings yahoo july     a b yahoocom site overview alexacom alexa internet retrieved march     verizon deal closes  yahoo era ends verizon closes  billion buyout  yahoo celebrates th anniversary yahoo news march   retrieved march     at  yahoo celebrates and looks ahead yahoo march   retrieved march     yahoo’s sale to verizon ends an era for a web pioneer the new york times july     perlroth nicole july   marissa mayer hopes to improve user experience at yahoo the times of india new delhi archived from the original on july     staff  yahoocom quantcast – its your audience we just find it quantcast corporation retrieved may     yahoocom analytics similarwebcom retrieved june     top  sites in the world for news and media similarwebcom retrieved june     swartz jon november   yahoos latest moves baffle some usa today washington dc retrieved july     canada pension plan mulls yahoo buy re